à¤£ à¤—à¤°à¥à¤¨,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;à¤¬à¥ˆà¤™à¥à¤•à¤¿à¤™à¥à¤— à¤¤à¤¥à¤¾ à¤µà¤¿à¤¤à¥à¤¤à¥€à¤¯ à¤ªà¥à¤°à¤£à¤¾à¤²à¥€à¤ªà¥à¤°à¤¤à¤¿ à¤µà¤¿à¤¶à¥à¤µà¤¸à¤¨à¥€à¤¯à¤¤à¤¾ à¤…à¤­à¤¿à¤µà¥ƒà¤¦à¥à¤§à¤¿ à¤—à¤°à¥à¤¨ à¤°</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;à¤¬à¥ˆà¤™à¥à¤•à¤¿à¤™à¥à¤— à¤•à¤¸à¥‚à¤° à¤¤à¤¥à¤¾ à¤¸à¤œà¤¾à¤¯à¤•à¤¾ à¤¸à¤®à¥à¤¬à¤¨à¥à¤§à¤®à¤¾ à¤•à¤¾à¤¨à¥‚à¤¨à¥€ à¤µà¥à¤¯à¤µà¤¸à¥à¤¥à¤¾ à¤—à¤°à¥à¤¨ à¥¤</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>à¤à¤¨ à¤…à¤¨à¥à¤¸à¤¾à¤°&nbsp;â€œà¤¢à¥à¤•à¥à¤Ÿà¥€à¤•à¥‹ à¤•à¤¾à¤°à¥‹à¤¬à¤¾à¤°â€&nbsp;à¤­à¤¨à¥à¤¨à¤¾à¤²à¥‡ à¤à¤• à¤†à¤ªà¤¸à¤®à¤¾ à¤°à¤•à¤® à¤‰à¤ à¤¾à¤ˆ à¤¸à¤¹à¤®à¤¤à¤¿à¤•à¤¾ à¤†à¤§à¤¾à¤°à¤®à¤¾ à¤†à¤²à¥‹à¤ªà¤¾à¤²à¥‹ à¤—à¤°à¥€ à¤°à¤•à¤® à¤²à¤¿à¤¨à¥‡ à¤µà¤¾ à¤¦à¤¿à¤¨à¥‡ à¤—à¤°à¥€ à¤—à¤°à¥‡à¤•à¥‹ à¤•à¤¾à¤°à¥‹à¤µà¤¾à¤° à¤¸à¤®à¥à¤à¤¨à¥ à¤ªà¤°à¥à¤› à¥¤ à¤¢à¥à¤•à¥à¤Ÿà¥€à¤•à¥‹ à¤•à¤¾à¤°à¥‹à¤¬à¤¾à¤°à¤²à¤¾à¤‡ à¤à¤¨à¤²à¥‡ à¤¬à¥ˆà¤‚à¤•à¤¿à¤™ à¤•à¤¸à¥‚à¤° à¤…à¤¨à¥à¤¤à¤°à¥à¤—à¤¤ à¤°à¤¾à¤–à¥‡à¤•à¥‹ à¤› à¤° à¤¢à¥à¤•à¥à¤Ÿà¥€à¤•à¥‹ à¤•à¤¾à¤°à¥‹à¤¬à¤¾à¤° à¤—à¤°à¥‡à¤®à¤¾ à¤•à¥ˆà¤¦ à¤° à¤¬à¤¿à¤—à¥‹ à¤­à¤°à¤¾à¤ˆ à¤¬à¤¿à¤—à¥‹ à¤¬à¤®à¥‹à¤œà¤¿à¤® à¤œà¤°à¤¿à¤µà¤¾à¤¨à¤¾ à¤—à¤°à¥à¤¨à¥‡ à¤µà¥à¤¯à¤µà¤¸à¥à¤¥à¤¾ à¤—à¤°à¥‡à¤•à¥‹ à¤› à¥¤</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Q.5. What are the main objectives of Banking Offence and Punishment Act?&nbsp;</strong><strong>How has the act defined \"<em>Dhukuti\"&nbsp;</em>transaction?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With the modern and expanding business in the banking sector, the banking sector has become synonymous with the economy. Due to voluminous transactions, there are possibilities of equal risks, theft, hacking etc. in banking industry. Banking Offence and Punishment Act was thus, needed to minimize the banking risks and take proper action against the offences.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The main objective of Banking Offence and Punishment Act, is given in the preamble of the Act which is given below:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;to minimize the effects and risks that may arise due to offences in banking and financial system transactions</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- to increase the credibility of the banking and financial systems</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- to make legal arrangements regarding banking offences and penalties.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As per the Act, \"<em>Dhukuti\"</em>&nbsp;transaction means the transaction of raising money by mutual agreements and to either give or take money on one to one basis. The Act has placed the business of Dhukti under the Banking Offences and has imposed penalty and imprisonment for such transaction.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Objectives of Banking Offence and Punishment Act, meaning of \"Dhukuti\" (5 marks)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-autosave-v1', '', '', '2021-10-24 08:06:15', '2021-10-24 08:06:15', '', 20, 'http://localhost/krishnablog/?p=151', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
