 given in the preamble of the Act which is given below:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-&nbsp;to minimize the effects and risks that may arise due to offences in banking and financial system transactions</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- to increase the credibility of the banking and financial systems</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- to make legal arrangements regarding banking offences and penalties.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As per the Act, \"<em>Dhukuti\"</em>&nbsp;transaction means the transaction of raising money by mutual agreements and to either give or take money on one to one basis. The Act has placed the business of Dhukti under the Banking Offences and has imposed penalty and imprisonment for such transaction.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Objectives of Banking Offence and Punishment Act, meaning of \"Dhukuti\" (5 marks)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-24 08:06:19', '2021-10-24 08:06:19', '', 20, 'http://localhost/krishnablog/?p=152', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
