<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>Ans. A central bank is an independent national authority that isues monetary policy, regulates banks, and provides financial services including economic research. Its goals are to stabilize the nation\'s currency, keep unemployment low, and prevent inflation.</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>The principles of central bank are as follows;</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;To work in the principle of national interest.</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Act as the monetary body of the country</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Perform open market operations</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Act as debt reservoir and lender of last resort</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Free from political interference</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Free from competition</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Act as a government banker</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>l&nbsp;&nbsp;Work as banker of commercial banks and financial institutions</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>In this way, Central bank acts to work as a supreme monetary authority of the nation by mobilizing the economy.</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->', 'Principles of Central Bank (5 marks, Nepal Bank Assistant)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '171-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-10-24 09:41:07', '2021-10-24 09:41:07', '', 171, 'http://localhost/krishnablog/?p=172', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
